{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act23side", "eventName": "登臨意", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "WB-2", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "沙海黃塵", "storyInfo": "左樂鬧市遇襲，幸得仇白的幫助才能脫險。老鯉誤打誤撞發現了槐天裴的蹤跡。林雨霞從走私商人那裡查到了一些線索，這讓她確信城外天災信使遇害別有隱情。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g10_yumenfair", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tense_intro", "key": "$tense_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽，媽，你快看，那邊好像有人在打架！", "name": "頑皮的小孩"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼好看的，談價談不攏就打起來了。", "name": "忙碌的女性"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟緊一點，在這裡走丟了，一會我都不知道該去哪找你。", "name": "忙碌的女性"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_297_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左公子，這夥人不會輕易甘休。再打下去，我們能不能自保先不說，很難保證不會傷及百姓。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#5$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......鯉先生，有什麼主意？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#6$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "逃跑的辦法倒是有，只怕後面會讓你不好收場啊......", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_297_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等——", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_297_1#4$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（糟糕，來不及——）", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#3$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bldwhoosh"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 2.0, "fillfrom": 0.0, "fillto": 0.6, "fadetime": 0.01, "grad": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 6.0, "fillfrom": 0.